content: प्रजन् {c4c} <ab>A.</ab> {@--1@} To be born or produced, come into existence. {@--2@} To grow, arise, spring up. {@--3@} To bring forth, be delivered of. {@--4@} To beget, generate, produce in general. {%--<ab>Caus.</ab>%} {@--1@} To beget, generate. {@--2@} To cause, produce. {@--3@} To bring forth, bear.
